Interface IceSoapParser<ReturnType>

Type Parameters:
ReturnType - The class of the object to return. For instance, if I wanted to return a "Product" object from this parser, I would specify {code } and override the resulting methods
All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseIceSoapParserImpl, IceSoapListParserImpl, IceSoapParserImpl
public interface IceSoapParser<ReturnType>

Interface for all parsers. Note that this parser is not the same concept as the XmlPullParser - rather, implementations of this class wrap around the XmlPullParser and use it to parse an instance of the ReturnType object.

Author:
Alex Gilleran
